@NODE WHAT "What is this?"

  A program that calculates your @{" Personality card " LINK PKORT}, @{" Soulcard " LINK SKORT}, and
  @{" Personal growth card " LINK VKORT}.

  Don't expect too much from this program. I made in an hour or two for fun
  after reading a book with the formula for calculating the cards.

@ENDNODE

@NODE HOWTO "How to use"

  Enter your birthdate (used by the calculation of the personality and
  soulcard) and the year you want to see your personal growth card of.

  Click on the check button to calculate, the ?-button will display the
  common interpretation of the card itself. The About gadget will show
  some information about this program.

@ENDNODE

@NODE REG "Registration"

  If you like, (please) send lots (or less) of money and you may
  consider yourself as an registred user.

@ENDNODE

