@NODE PKORT "Personality card"

  The personality card shows a persons qualities which are going to
  be developed during the persons lifetime. It's these qualities we
  the rest of the world see's in you, it's the way we use to change
  the world around us. This card shows how we are acting towards other
  people, what missions we have to accomplish in the world, and which
  challanges we are going to meet.


  Swedish translation:

  Personlighetskortet visar de kvaliteter hos personen som ska
  utvecklas. Det ðr dessa kvaliteter vi —ppet visar vðrlden, de
  medel vi anvðnder f—r att pÍverka vðrlden runt oss. Detta
  kort visar oss hur vi ter oss utÍt, vilka uppgifter vi mÍste
  slutf—ra i vðrlden, och vilka utmaningar vi kommer att m—ta.

@ENDNODE

@NODE SKORT "Soulcard"

  The soulcard shows what inner qualitites which are going to be
  developed. These are the hidden powers we use to find our way, the
  way to our true self, to the inner master.


  Swedish translation:

  Sjðlskortet visar vilka inre kvaliteter som ska utvecklas. Dessa
  ðr de g—mda krafter med vilka vi finner vÍr vðg, vðgen till vÍrt
  sanna sjðlv, till den inre mðstaren.

@ENDNODE

@NODE VKORT "Personal growth card"

  The card for personal growth shows the energies, missions, challanges,
  step in personal developement, etc., that will be especially common
  during the selected year.


  Swedish translation:

  Kortet f—r Personligt Vðxande visar de energier, uppgifter,
  utmaningar, steg i utvecklingen, etc., som ðr genomgÍende
  under sðrskilda Ír i ditt liv.

@ENDNODE
